listening to people yell!

267
00:09:29.903 --> 00:09:31.238
-[laughs]
-What?

268
00:09:31.321 --> 00:09:32.239
You're yelling.

269
00:09:32.322 --> 00:09:33.949
[laughs]

270
00:09:34.032 --> 00:09:35.284
You're actually yelling.

271
00:09:35.367 --> 00:09:36.868
[laughs]

272
