but I don't remember.

280
00:09:51.383 --> 00:09:52.593
That art gallery in town.

281
00:09:52.676 --> 00:09:53.594
Yeah.

282
00:09:53.677 --> 00:09:54.720
Lia's friend...

283
00:09:54.803 --> 00:09:55.679
[doorbell rings]
-She had a piece. yeah.

284
00:09:55.762 --> 00:09:56.763
I'll grab it.

285
00:09:56.846 --> 00:09:58.473
I'll grab it.

286
00:09:58.556 --> 00:09:59.808
So. an art gallery?

287
00:09:59.891 --> 00:10:01.476
And it was someone you knew?

288
00:10:01.559 --> 00:10:03.520
I... I was trying to be a
supportive friend to her.

289
00:10:03.603 --> 00:10:04.855
Uh-huh.

290
00:10:04.938 --> 00:10:06.773
Why didn't you
tell the detective?

291
00:10:06.856 --> 00:10:08.650
Who was that?

292
00:10:08.733 --> 00:10:11.820
Oh. it's. uh...

293
00:10:11.903 --> 00:10:14.781
<i>[somber music]</i>

294
00:10:14.864 --> 00:10:21.996
