303
00:10:58.867 --> 00:11:00.452
Everybody just.
can you stop. please?

304
00:11:00.535 --> 00:11:01.954
No. what the fuck is
going on is that no one ever

305
00:11:02.037 --> 00:11:03.622
calls you out.
-Calls me out on what?

306
00:11:03.705 --> 00:11:04.665
And I am so sick of...
