307
00:11:04.748 --> 00:11:07.084
I wanna clean the couch!

308
00:11:07.167 --> 00:11:07.960
What?

309
00:11:08.043 --> 00:11:09.294
I want to clean the couch.

310
00:11:09.377 --> 00:11:12.714
And we're out of
upholstery cleaner.

311
00:11:12.797 --> 00:11:13.924
Mar. "Real Insight"
is not gonna care

312
00:11:14.007 --> 00:11:15.092
