313
00:11:15.175 --> 00:11:16.426
I care!

314
00:11:16.509 --> 00:11:18.720
Can you please go and
get upholstery cleaner?

315
00:11:21.556 --> 00:11:26.103
Yep. sure.

316
00:11:26.186 --> 00:11:29.481
Um. yeah.

317
00:11:38.114 --> 00:11:42.661
