323
00:12:26.162 --> 00:12:28.290
Happy Birthday. sweetheart.

324
00:12:28.373 --> 00:12:35.296
<i>♪♪</i>

325
00:12:39.968 --> 00:12:43.430
<i>[unsettling music]</i>

326
00:12:43.513 --> 00:12:50.478
<i>♪♪</i>

327
00:12:52.147 --> 00:12:53.482
<i>This is the Lemon Drop Gallery.</i>

328
00:12:53.565 --> 00:12:55.442
<i>Please leave a message
after the tone.</i>

329
00:12:55.525 --> 00:12:57.903
Hi. uh. I was
wondering if someone

330
00:12:57.986 --> 00:12:59.446
