336
00:13:13.460 --> 00:13:15.712
Marissa has an interview
with "Real Insight" at 8:00.

337
00:13:15.795 --> 00:13:17.798
And she wanted me to
come over to go over some

338
00:13:17.881 --> 00:13:19.383
