339
00:13:19.466 --> 00:13:20.884
<i>Well. are you staying
for the actual interview?</i>

340
00:13:20.967 --> 00:13:22.803
<i>Or are you leaving by then?</i>

341
00:13:22.886 --> 00:13:24.221
I don't... I don't know.

342
00:13:24.304 --> 00:13:26.014
Why is it such a big deal?

343
00:13:26.097 --> 00:13:27.557
Well. I just...

344
00:13:27.640 --> 00:13:28.892
I just want to know if
you're doing Jacob's bath

345
00:13:28.975 --> 00:13:30.060
or if I'm still on duty. then.

346
00:13:30.143 --> 00:13:32.854
That's all.

347
00:13:32.937 --> 00:13:34.273
<i>What?</i>

348
00:13:34.356 --> 00:13:37.192
Why are you always
so eager to get free?

349
00:13:37.275 --> 00:13:39.444
<i>You always want to know
when you'll be "off."</i>

350
00:13:39.527 --> 00:13:41.905
That's a real shitty
thing to say. Jen. OK?

351
00:13:41.988 --> 00:13:43.407
You know I love my son.

352
00:13:43.490 --> 00:13:44.992
Whenever you're left
in charge of Jacob.

353
00:13:45.075 --> 00:13:47.411
you always want to
know when it'll end.

354
00:13:47.494 --> 00:13:50.330
