367
00:14:16.231 --> 00:14:19.901
So I don't actually
have any time off.

368
00:14:19.984 --> 00:14:23.530
I... I don't know what you
expect me to say. or do.

369
00:14:23.613 --> 00:14:25.782
It feels like you
just always need more.

370
00:14:25.865 --> 00:14:27.951
This is never enough.

371
00:14:28.034 --> 00:14:29.870
<i>I mean. come on. Jen.
a big part of who I am</i>

372
00:14:29.953 --> 00:14:32.289
<i>is that I need some space
and some freedom. you know?</i>

373
00:14:32.372 --> 00:14:33.999
<i>That's what you used
to love about me.</i>

374
00:14:34.082 --> 00:14:35.709
<i>I do my own thing.</i>

375
00:14:35.792 --> 00:14:37.961
I mean. I should still be
allowed to be me. you know.

376
00:14:38.044 --> 00:14:39.296
even though we have a child.

377
00:14:39.379 --> 00:14:40.881
Like. I didn't sign
up for this whole

378
00:14:40.964 --> 00:14:43.717
