407
00:16:17.143 --> 00:16:19.730
OK.

408
00:16:19.813 --> 00:16:25.569
The man who's with
Carrie Finch. she...

409
00:16:25.652 --> 00:16:26.820
she executed him.

410
00:16:29.322 --> 00:16:32.242
The woman who has my son
is violent and armed.

411
00:16:34.994 --> 00:16:36.079
I did this.

412
00:16:36.162 --> 00:16:37.748
No. No. no. no.

413
00:16:37.831 --> 00:16:39.082
-I did this to your family.
-No. Jenny. that's not...

414
00:16:39.165 --> 00:16:40.792
If I hadn't hired her...

415
00:16:40.875 --> 00:16:42.085
It's not your fault. It's...
that's the thing. it's not.

416
00:16:42.168 --> 00:16:44.546
She knew him from before.

417
00:16:44.629 --> 00:16:45.964
What?

418
00:16:46.047 --> 00:16:48.842
Yeah. she knew Milo from
before you even hired her.

419
00:16:48.925 --> 00:16:50.468
It's not your fault.

420
00:16:53.179 --> 00:16:55.641
So this was the plan?

421
00:16:55.724 --> 00:16:58.769
She wanted to work for
me to get close to Milo?

422
00:16:58.852 --> 00:17:00.103
I don't know.

423
00:17:00.186 --> 00:17:07.360
<i>♪♪</i>

424
00:17:09.696 --> 00:17:12.991
What's my favorite
thing about Milo?

425
00:17:13.074 --> 00:17:17.162
Oh. uh. "Real Insight"
are gonna be here at 8:00.

426
00:17:17.245 --> 00:17:19.081
And they're gonna
ask me that question.

427
00:17:19.164 --> 00:17:20.374
so I need to think
about my answer.

428
00:17:20.457 --> 00:17:21.875
But I don't...
I don't want to think

429
00:17:21.958 --> 00:17:24.962
about it. because it'll
make me break down.

430
00:17:25.045 --> 00:17:29.132
You don't have to think about
the answer to that question.

431
00:17:29.215 --> 00:17:30.259
You already know it.

432
00:17:30.342 --> 00:17:33.887
[scoffs] Yeah.

433
00:17:37.015 --> 00:17:39.768
I have to keep busy.

434
00:17:39.851 --> 00:17:41.728
It's... it helps.

435
00:17:41.811 --> 00:17:43.230
OK.

436
00:17:43.313 --> 00:17:45.983
Let's be busy.

437
00:17:46.066 --> 00:17:47.818
