441
00:17:58.286 --> 00:17:59.955
Yeah.

442
00:18:00.038 --> 00:18:02.165
Can we do the whole thing?

443
00:18:02.248 --> 00:18:04.376
Sure.

444
00:18:04.459 --> 00:18:07.379
Do you mind staying for a while?

445
00:18:09.214 --> 00:18:10.173
As long as you want.

446
00:18:10.256 --> 00:18:12.843
